## Real-World Impact

### Before Docker:
- "It works on my machine!" problems
- Environment inconsistencies
- Long setup times for new developers
- Difficult dependency management
- Slow deployment cycles

### After Docker:
- "It works everywhere!" guarantee
- Identical environments across dev, test, prod
- Minutes setup time for new developers
- Clean dependency isolation
- Fast, reliable deployments

